config MFD_S2MPS34
	tristate "Samsung S2MPS34 PMIC core driver"
	depends on I2C
	depends on OF
	select REGMAP_I2C
	select MFD_CORE
	default y
	help
	  This enables the Samsung S2MPS34 PMIC core driver. The S2MPS34
	  is the PMIC for the Samsung Exynos 1280 (s5e8825) SoC, providing
	  39 LDOs, 9 BUCK regulators, RTC, and watchdog.

	  The PMIC is accessed via I2C through the ACPM MFD bus
	  (an I2C-over-ACPM-IPC tunnel) or a direct I2C bus.

	  Must be enabled for the S2MPS34 regulator and RTC drivers.
